OL,3,CEx-church warden has murder conviction
OL,4,Cquashed at Court of Appeal
OL,6,FA former church warden who was jailed
OL,7,Ffor life for the murder of a
OL,8,Funiversity lecturer has had his
OL,9,Fconviction quashed at the Court of
OL,10,FAppeal.
OL,12,FBenjamin Field was jailed for at least
OL,13,F36 years in 2019 after being found
OL,14,Fguilty of murdering 69-year-old Peter
OL,15,FFarquhar in Maids Moreton,
OL,16,FBuckinghamshire.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
