PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776420366
OL,3,CEx-church warden has murder conviction
OL,4,Cquashed at Court of Appeal
OL,6,FProsecutors told Field's trial that he
OL,7,Fhad driven Mr Farquhar to think he was
OL,8,Flosing his mind in order to inherit
OL,9,Fhis house and money, secretly giving
OL,10,Fthe pensioner tranquiliser drugs and
OL,11,Fspiking his whisky in the hope that
OL,12,Fhis death in 2015 would look like
OL,13,Fsuicide or an accident.
OL,15,FThe case was referred to the Court of
OL,16,FAppeal by the Criminal Cases Review
OL,17,FCommission last year, with Field's
OL,18,Flawyers telling a hearing in March
OL,19,Fthat there was "no evidence" that Mr
OL,20,FFarquhar was "forced or deceived" into
OL,21,Ftaking the whisky or medication.
OL,26,@{D@POU{D@\O]|D@NOU|D@aO]
