CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776420366
OL,3,CEx-church warden has murder conviction
OL,4,Cquashed at Court of Appeal
OL,6,FIn a ruling on Thursday, three senior
OL,7,Fjudges quashed the conviction and
OL,8,Fordered a retrial.
OL,10,FReading a summary of their ruling,
OL,11,FLord Justice Edis, sitting with Mr
OL,12,FJustice Goose and Mr Justice Butcher,
OL,13,Fsaid the jurors at trial had "not been
OL,14,Fproperly directed", and the directions
OL,15,Fgiven to them on how to reach a
OL,16,Fverdict were "defective".
OL,18,FHe said: "The directions effectively
OL,19,Fwithdrew from the jury the question of
OL,20,Fwhether Mr Farquhar's decision to
OL,21,Fdrink the whisky had been voluntary."
OL,26,@uD@^OUvD@RO]xD@NOUxD@XO]zD@JOU}D@eO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
