PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776420366
OL,3,CEx-church warden has murder conviction
OL,4,Cquashed at Court of Appeal
OL,6,FLord Justice Edis also said the Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service (CPS) could take
OL,8,Fthe "unusual case" to the Supreme
OL,9,FCourt before any retrial.
OL,11,FThe judge added that Field will remain
OL,12,Fin prison "for so long as the appeal
OL,13,F(to the Supreme Court) is pending".
OL,26,@pD@EOUpD@RO]tD@KOUuD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
