PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776420366
OL,3,CEx-church warden has murder conviction
OL,4,Cquashed at Court of Appeal
OL,6,FBefore his murder trial at Oxford
OL,7,FCrown Court, Field admitted two counts
OL,8,Fof burglary and three of fraud after
OL,9,Ffraudulently being in relationships
OL,10,Fwith both Mr Farquhar and his
OL,11,Fneighbour, fellow pensioner Ann Moore-
OL,12,FMartin, as part of a plan to get them
OL,13,Fto change their wills.
OL,15,FJurors heard Field underwent a
OL,16,F"betrothal" ceremony with Mr Farquhar
OL,17,Fwhile also having a string of
OL,18,Fgirlfriends and a relationship with
OL,19,FMiss Moore-Martin.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
