FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776420366
OL,3,CEx-church warden has murder conviction
OL,4,Cquashed at Court of Appeal
OL,6,FThe trial was told that the Baptist
OL,7,Fminister's son had manipulated Miss
OL,8,FMoore-Martin, a deeply religious
OL,9,Fretired head teacher who died from
OL,10,Fnatural causes in May 2017, by writing
OL,11,Fmessages on her mirrors purporting to
OL,12,Fbe from God.
OL,14,FField, of Wellingborough Road, Olney,
OL,15,FBuckinghamshire, was later convicted
OL,16,Fof Mr Farquhar's murder but cleared of
OL,17,Fconspiring or attempting to murder
OL,18,FMiss Moore-Martin, and found not
OL,19,Fguilty of possession of an article for
OL,20,Fuse in fraud.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776420366
OL,3,CEx-church warden has murder conviction
OL,4,Cquashed at Court of Appeal
OL,6,FAlongside his life sentence, he was
OL,7,Fgiven a concurrent 16-year jail term
OL,8,Ffor the fraud and burglary offences.
OL,10,FThe case was later turned into a BBC
OL,11,Fdrama, The Sixth Commandment, starring
OL,12,FTimothy Spall and Eanna Hardwicke.
OL,14,FField lost an attempt to appeal
OL,15,Fagainst his conviction in 2021, but
OL,16,Fhis lawyers told a hearing in London
OL,17,Flast month that the previous Court of
OL,18,FAppeal decision wrongly applied the
OL,19,Flaw due to "moral disapproval".
OL,26,@{D@LOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
