FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776420366
OL,3,CEx-church warden has murder conviction
OL,4,Cquashed at Court of Appeal
OL,6,FDavid Jeremy KC, for Field, told the
OL,7,Fhearing that his client would have had
OL,8,Fto have caused Mr Farquhar to ingest
OL,9,Fthe whisky or medication, as well as
OL,10,Fit being "less than fully voluntary",
OL,11,Fto have caused the death.
OL,13,FHe said that Mr Farquhar "knew what he
OL,14,Fwas being given and knew who he was
OL,15,Fbeing given it by", and that the
OL,16,Fsituation was akin to "causing him to
OL,17,Fdrive his car by handing him his car
OL,18,Fkeys".
OL,26,@rD@JOUrD@dO]uD@ZOUwD@RO]xD@WOUzD@EO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
