FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776420366
OL,3,CEx-church warden has murder conviction
OL,4,Cquashed at Court of Appeal
OL,6,FThe Crown Prosecution Service opposed
OL,7,Fthe appeal, with KC David Perry
OL,8,Fclaiming Field was "not a mere
OL,9,Fbystander or a mere spectator of Mr
OL,10,FFarquhar's death at his own hands".
OL,12,F"He was, at all times, playing his
OL,13,Fpart in causing the death both as a
OL,14,Fmatter of common sense and as a matter
OL,15,Fof law," the barrister said.
OL,26,@pD@TOUrD@bO]tD@AOUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
